---

<style is:inline>
  .modeule-display-none {
    display: none !important;
  }
</style>

<MasterLayout>
  <HomeHero
    classes="modeule-display-nonex"
    title="Hi, I'm Glen, a Front-End Developer."
    body="Turning Design into Reality with Clean, Accessible Code."
    cta="Contact"
  />
  <div class="container module modeule-display-nonex">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 mx-auto">
        <p>
          With 8 years of proven experience in e-commerce, I've had the
          privilege of contributing to industry-leading brands and building a
          skill set that spans HTML5, CSS3, Javascript, JQuery, and React. From
          building and deploying content to ensuring clean, performant code, I
          always strive to uphold the latest industry standards.
        </p>
        <p>
          Over my 15 years as a designer, I've developed strong design
          principles that enable me to execute pixel-perfect work every time.
          Whether it's web design, UI/UX, or graphic design, my work always
          prioritizes user experience and aesthetics. For example, I recently
          led a redesign of a popular e-commerce site that resulted in a 20%
          increase in conversion rates.
        </p>
        <p>
          My technical skills are complemented by strong soft skills such as
          communication, collaboration, and problem-solving. I value working
          closely with stakeholders to ensure their vision is translated into a
          final product that exceeds their expectations.
        </p>
        <p>
          By combining my technical expertise, design principles, and soft
          skills, I bring a unique perspective to every project I work on.
          Whether it's improving website performance, creating a new user
          experience, or developing a brand identity, I'm passionate about
          delivering exceptional results that exceed expectations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container module modeule-display-nonex">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-10 col-lg-6 mx-auto">
        <div class="skill-tag-wrapper">
          {skills.map((skill) => <SkillTag key={skill} title={skill} />)}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container module modeule-display-nonex">
    <hr class="divider-decoration" />
  </div>

  <div class="container px-0 module modeule-display-nonex">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-11 col-lg-10 mx-auto">
        <h2 class="h4 section-title text-center">Some things Iâ€™ve created.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col col-12">
        <div class="card-container mx-auto mt-4">
          {
            myWork.map((card) => (
              <Card
                href={card.href}
                title={card.title}
                body={card.body}
                img={card.img}
                cta={card.cta}
              />
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container module">
    <h2 class="text-center">Some nice words about me.</h2>
    <div class="quote quote-top">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"
        ><!--! Font Awesome Pro 6.4.0 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license (Commercial License) Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc. -->
        <path
          d="M0 216C0 149.7 53.7 96 120 96h8c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32s-14.3 32-32 32h-8c-30.9 0-56 25.1-56 56v8h64c35.3 0 64 28.7 64 64v64c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64H64c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64V320 288 216zm256 0c0-66.3 53.7-120 120-120h8c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32s-14.3 32-32 32h-8c-30.9 0-56 25.1-56 56v8h64c35.3 0 64 28.7 64 64v64c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64H320c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64V320 288 216z"
        ></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonials-wrapper">
      <div class="testimonial">
        <div class="testimonial-person">
          <div class="testimonial-person-name">
            {testimonials[0].name}
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-person-title">
            {testimonials[0].title}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-body">
          <p>{testimonials[0].quote}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote quote-bottom">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"
          ><!--! Font Awesome Pro 6.4.0 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license (Commercial License) Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc. -->
          <path
            d="M448 296c0 66.3-53.7 120-120 120h-8c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32h8c30.9 0 56-25.1 56-56v-8H320c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64V160c0-35.3 28.7-64 64-64h64c35.3 0 64 28.7 64 64v32 32 72zm-256 0c0 66.3-53.7 120-120 120H64c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32h8c30.9 0 56-25.1 56-56v-8H64c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64V160c0-35.3 28.7-64 64-64h64c35.3 0 64 28.7 64 64v32 32 72z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script>
      const swiper = new Swiper(".swiper", {
        autoplay: {
          delay: 5000, // time between each slide transition in milliseconds
          disableOnInteraction: true, // enable or disable the autoplay when user interacts with the swiper
        },
        navigation: {
          nextEl: ".swiper-button-next",
          prevEl: ".swiper-button-prev",
        },
      });
    </script>
  </div>
</MasterLayout>
